{
  "description": "A coastal scene featuring rocky intertidal zones and a prominent sea stack. The foreground is filled with dark, wet rocks of varying sizes, covered in what appears to be algae or seaweed.  Water pools amongst the rocks, reflecting the sky.  In the midground, a large, sculpted sea stack rises from the water, its surface textured and uneven. Beyond the sea stack, the ocean extends towards the horizon under a clear, blue sky.  A faint coastline is visible in the far distance. The water is a mix of deep blue and foamy white near the rocks, suggesting gentle waves. Overall, the image depicts a rugged and natural coastal environment.",
